race.comment: LACIE ACE (12) was building towards her last start win, scoring by 0.3L after settling midfield over the 1400m journey here. Tsang remains in the saddle, meaning she carries no weight after the claim. Out to the mile now looks ideal and she can bring up back-to-back wins. ZADOWS LANDING (6) is looking for the hat-trick today after a good win over this track and trip 15 days ago. He was just too strong late in the race and this looks to shape similarly. Likely to be back in the run again, but should be flying late. HEAVENBENT (11) is better than she showed last start when going around in tougher company than what she'll face today. Her record over this course and distance is solid and she'll be able to sit closer this time around. Will be hard to hold down. SNIPPERANDO (3) is third-up now and out in trip where she was a big winner last campaign. Can sit handy and build on her latest effort. RAZMAS (5) has to be included on his recent form.
